Algal densities of light green mediums were calibrated from OD using the values of algal densities with their respective ODs of dark green mediums. If OD of the light green medium is x1 and ODs and algal densities of two dark green medium are x2 and x3, and y2 and y3, respectively; algal density of light green medium y1 is calculated by the linear interpolation Eq. (2).2y1-y2/y2-y3=x1-x2/x2-x3\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
